      "seed": 1041147768,
      "version": 1002,
      "versionNonce": 2015295752,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769927911254,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ticketmaster(BookMyShow)\n\nFR: \n1. Show Events\n2. Search for events\n3. Book Tickets\n\nBelow the line: \n1. user being able to see his booked tickets\n2. admins being able to add events\n3. dynamic pricing for popular events \n\n\nNFR:\n1. Availability for searching and viewing events, consistency for booking tickets\n2. Scale and be able to handle high througput in terms of popular event\n3. Search should be low latency\n4. Should be read heavy, should be able to handle high read throughput.\n\nBelow the Line\n1. protect user data\n2. fault tolerence\n3. provide secure transactions for purchases\n4. well tested and easy to deploy\n5. should have regular backups",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ticketmaster(BookMyShow)\n\nFR: \n1. Show Events\n2. Search for events\n3. Book Tickets\n\nBelow the line: \n1. user being able to see his booked tickets\n2. admins being able to add events\n3. dynamic pricing for popular events \n\n\nNFR:\n1. Availability for searching and viewing events, consistency for booking tickets\n2. Scale and be able to handle high througput in terms of popular event\n3. Search should be low latency\n4. Should be read heavy, should be able to handle high read throughput.\n\nBelow the Line\n1. protect user data\n2. fault tolerence\n3. provide secure transactions for purchases\n4. well tested and easy to deploy\n5. should have regular backups",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dsC8y-kPLF_L2YRxLwjlH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 817.09765625,
      "y": 267.994140625,
      "width": 129.29991149902344,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
